# 🤖 Agentic AI Framework

An autonomous AI agent system built with **LangChain** and **LlamaIndex**, designed to reason, plan, and execute multi-step tasks using external tools, APIs, and data sources.

## 🚀 Features

- **Autonomous Task Execution** – Breaks down complex goals into actionable steps
- **Tool Integration** – Connects to APIs, databases, and external services
- **Memory & Context** – Maintains conversation history and long-term memory
- **RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)** – Uses LlamaIndex for document/knowledge retrieval
- **Modular Architecture** – Easily extend with custom tools and agents
- **LLM Agnostic** – Compatible with OpenAI, Anthropic, and other providers

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Language:** Python 3.10+
- **Frameworks:** LangChain, LlamaIndex
- **LLM Provider:** [OpenAI / Anthropic / Local models]
- **Vector Store:** [Pinecone / Chroma / FAISS]
- **Other:** [Any additional libraries]

